Aaron Paul is a three-time Emmy Award–winning actor you know from his iconic performance as Jesse Pinkman in Breaking Bad. Check out Dos Hombres mezcal for your smooth and smoky cocktails this summer, and catch his starring role in the sci-fi thriller, Ash, which is now available on demand and streaming. But how is he with spicy food? Find out as Paul takes on the wings of death and discusses Breaking Bad lore, Bryan Cranston's most memorable on-set pranks, and his appearance on The Price Is Right.
